Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_scheduler.course.Activity
      • edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_scheduler.course.Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Conflict
    public class Event
extends Activity
    An object extended from the Activity class which is added to WolfScheduler as an Event Will be used through WolfScheduler for the client to create a schedule getShortDisplayArray and getLongDisplayArray are used to output contents of the event for the client to view isDuplicate compares 2 events to see if they're the same
    Author:
    yash
